Package application

The application package stores all necessary files for our Movie Gen7000 project.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    Application file.
    Controller
    This class is the action controller for the FXML file.
    Main
    Main file for the project.
    MovieDBAccount
    Creates an account which links with an existing movie database account.
    MovieSelection
    This class is linked with a current MovieDBAccount and holds that accounts currently selected movie.
    SearchModule
    This class links with an existing MovieDBAccount object and is used to perform search queries from the database for the current account.
    TmdbRandomizer
    This class links with an existing MovieDBAccount and is used to generate a random movie pool which the user can draw from for suggestions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataBaseConnectionException
    Exception thrown when a connection to the movie data was interrupted or never made.
    RandomNotFoundException
    This exception is thrown when a random movie pool was not created or the resulting pool was null.
    UserDataExemptException
    This exception is thrown when database data is used in place of user data.
